FAQ

Q: Why not paid access on the game page?
A: Many many people would need to purchase the game a second time in order to play. We do not want to do that. So until Roblox tells us we cannot continue with this model, we shall till beta.

Q: When does the open beta come out?
A: Our current goal is May 2024, however this may change if we feel we need more time.

Q: If I purchased paid access before, will I need to pay again?
A: Nope! You'll just be able to play.

Q: If I purchase the alpha, will I need to buy the beta too?
A: Nope, the beta will be free!

Q: Is there wallclimb boosting?
A: Yes.
